Struct janus_aggregator::cache::PeerAggregatorCache

source · 
pub struct PeerAggregatorCache { /* private fields */ }
Expand description

Caches taskprov PeerAggregator’s. This cache is never invalidated, so the process needs to be restarted if there are any changes to peer aggregators.
